  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1ECB ti\xEAn tri gi\xE0 k\xEAu l\xEAn c\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\u1EE7a Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF t\u1EEB Giu-\u0111a \u0111\u1EBFn, \"CH\xDAA n\xF3i r\u1EB1ng anh kh\xF4ng v\xE2ng l\u1EDDi Ng\xE0i! Ng\xE0i b\u1EA3o anh kh\xF4ng l\xE0m theo \u0111i\u1EC1u CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF truy\u1EC1n d\u1EB7n. "), mdx("h6", {
